{"tid":2421140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德法院向敘利亞酷刑判罪 全球首例","createTime":"2021-02-24T10:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T10:58:26.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c424d9cb4be4e4fe03fd44955a23a567fd7deee9","tid":2421140,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"德法院向敘利亞酷刑判罪 全球首例<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2021/02/Folterhelfer.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F02%2FFolterhelfer.html&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8DyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=249aa15d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2021/02/Folterhelfer.html</a><br />\n<br />\n德國 Koblenz 市的法院今天（24日）就一名前敘利亞秘密警察在敘國干犯酷刑行為而判刑，是全球首宗向敘利亞阿薩德政權的官員或軍警殘害平民進行判刑，因此案件受到全球關注。<br />\n<br />\n這次被定罪的是44歲男子Eyad al-Gharib，他被指在2011年拘捕一些反政府示威者，押送他們到秘密拘留所，而被捕者在拘留所面對酷刑虐待，部份甚至死亡，因此 al-Gharib 被判違反人道罪及協助他人違反人道罪罪名成立，入獄4年半。<br />\n<br />\n同案還有一名更高級的前敘利亞秘密警察、58歲Anwar Raslan，法院決定把二人分開審理，Raslan的案件預料要審訊至今年秋季，他被指在2011-12年間，虐待至少4000名敘利亞人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">德國2002年修改法例，對一些違反國際法的行為，包括種族滅絕、違反人類罪及戰爭罪行，擁有「全球司法管轄」（universal jurisdiction），亦即就算加害者、被害者及事發地點都不在德國，德國法院同樣可以審理及判刑。<br />\n<br />\n這次兩人被捕，是因為他們逃到德國，申請難民資格。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n敘利亞國內現時不可能對政府人員的暴行進行審判，國際法院不能受理，聯合國也不大可能另設特別法庭處理，因此在歐洲國家作出這類起訴，是敘利亞受害者目前把加害者繩之於法的唯一途徑。<br />\n<br />\n全球司法管轄不是新事物。二十多年前，西班牙起訴智利前獨裁者皮諾切特（Augusto Pinochet），英國應西班牙引渡要求而拘捕當時身在英國的皮諾切特，引發英國、西班牙與智利之間的外交糾紛，這是近年最轟動的全球司法管轄事件。<br />\n<br />\n這類案件充滿政治性。有人曾在比利時提出，引用此法審訊發動伊拉克戰爭的美國總統喬治布殊（George W. Bush），美國向比利時強力施壓後，比利時檢控部門不處理此案。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n全文請前往歐洲動態"},{"pid":"91393f57abdd5341a6c9495495eae0ff8a2bc964","tid":2421140,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63052f4b1b3fbef3a04ff16cbb67d0128c68ba34","tid":2421140,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">「全球司法管轄」（universal jurisdiction）</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁似香港國安法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc3cc1828d5e061daea44f6634de9460c5b107c","tid":2421140,"uid":284626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"63052f4b1b3fbef3a04ff16cbb67d0128c68ba34","tid":2421140,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">「全球司法管轄」（universal jurisdiction）</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁似香港國安法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"呢啲大既戰爭罪行/crimes against humanity係有呢個玩法的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係國際法庭點做嘢"},{"pid":"2b0c0aea09e8165d4df0bda4f79ccd8910bf55c2","tid":2421140,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"全球首例？中國歷史上打仗成日都識話係要解救人地國家於水深火熱之中啦"}]}